{"data":[{"name":"75:1","price":"我以复活日盟誓，","arabic":"لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5552,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:2","price":"我以自责的灵魂盟誓，","arabic":"وَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5553,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:3","price":"难道人猜想我绝不能集合他的骸骨吗？","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5554,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:4","price":"不然，〔我将集合他的骸骨〕，而且能使他的每个手指复原。","arabic":"بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5555,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:5","price":"不然，人欲长此放荡下去。","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفۡجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5556,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:6","price":"他问复活日在什么时候。","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5557,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:7","price":"当眼目昏花，","arabic":"فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5558,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:8","price":"月亮昏暗，","arabic":"وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5559,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:9","price":"日月相合的时候，","arabic":"وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5560,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:10","price":"在那日，人将说：“逃到哪里去呢？”","arabic":"يَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَيۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5561,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:11","price":"绝不然，绝无任何避难所。","arabic":"كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5562,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:12","price":"在那日，唯你的养主那里，有安定之所。","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5563,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:13","price":"在那日，各人将被告知自己前前后后做过的事情。","arabic":"يُنَبَّؤُاْ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5564,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:14","price":"不然，各人对自己就是明证，","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفۡسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5565,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:15","price":"即使他多方托辞。","arabic":"وَلَوۡ أَلۡقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5566,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:16","price":"你不必急于诵读而鼓动你的舌头。","arabic":"لَا تُحَرِّكۡ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعۡجَلَ بِهِۦٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5567,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:17","price":"集合它和诵读它，确是我的责任。","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا جَمۡعَهُۥ وَقُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5568,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:18","price":"当我诵读它的时候，你当静听我的诵读。","arabic":"فَإِذَا قَرَأۡنَٰهُ فَٱتَّبِعۡ قُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5569,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:19","price":"然后解释它，也是我的责任。","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا بَيَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5570,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:20","price":"真的，你们喜爱现世的生活，","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُحِبُّونَ ٱلۡعَاجِلَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5571,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:21","price":"而不顾后世的生活。","arabic":"وَتَذَرُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5572,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:22","price":"在那日，许多面目是光华的，","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاضِرَةٌ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5573,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:23","price":"是仰视着他们的养主的。","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5574,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:24","price":"在那日，许多面目是愁苦的，","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بَاسِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5575,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:25","price":"他们确信自己必遭大难。","arabic":"تَظُنُّ أَن يُفۡعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5576,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:26","price":"真的，〔灵魂〕达到锁骨时，","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلتَّرَاقِيَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5577,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:27","price":"有人说：“谁是祝由的？”","arabic":"وَقِيلَ مَنۡۜ رَاقٖ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5578,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:28","price":"他确信那是离别。","arabic":"وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ ٱلۡفِرَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5579,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:29","price":"〔死时〕胫与胫相缠结。","arabic":"وَٱلۡتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5580,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:30","price":"在那日，他只被驱赶到你的养主那里。","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمَسَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5581,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:31","price":"他没有归信，也没有礼拜。","arabic":"فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5582,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:32","price":"但他却否认了，他背弃了，","arabic":"وَلَٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5583,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:33","price":"然后他傲慢地走回自己的家去。","arabic":"ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5584,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:34","price":"“毁灭已逐渐地临近你。","arabic":"أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5585,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:35","price":"然后，毁灭已逐渐地临近你。”","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5586,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:36","price":"难道人猜想自己是被放任的吗？","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَن يُتۡرَكَ سُدًى","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5587,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:37","price":"难道他不曾是被射出的精液吗？","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَكُ نُطۡفَةٗ مِّن مَّنِيّٖ يُمۡنَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5588,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:38","price":"然后，他变成血块，而安拉加以创造他，使之成为肢体完全的人吗？","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةٗ فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5589,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:39","price":"他用精液造化两性，男的和女的。","arabic":"فَجَعَلَ مِنۡهُ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5590,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"75:40","price":"难道那样的造化者不能使死人复活吗？","arabic":"أَلَيۡسَ ذَٰلِكَ بِقَٰدِرٍ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحۡـِۧيَ ٱلۡمَوۡتَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5591,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah","Chapter Al-Qiyamah","Qiyamah","Surah Qiyamah","Chapter Qiyamah","Al Qiyamah","Surah Al Qiyamah","Chapter Al Qiyamah","Surah 75","Chapter 75","The Resurrection","القيامة"]}